                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-primary py-4">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="promo py-0">
                        <h2 class="promo-title h6">Subscribe to upload and watch premium videos at gameforest!</h2>
                        <a class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm ml-4" href="https://themeforest.net/item/gameforest-responsive-gaming-html-theme/5007730" target="_blank" role="button">Subscribe Now <i class="ya ya-share"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-6">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-8 mx-auto text-center mb-4">
                    <i class="ya ya-player icon"></i>
                    <h2 class="font-size-lg">Premium videos on gameforest</h2>
                    <p>Months on ye at by esteem desire warmth former. Sure that that way gave any fond now. His boy middleton sir nor engrossed affection excellent.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row row-md">
                {% for video in videos %}
                    {% if loop.index < 5 %}
                        <div class="col-3 card-group mb-4">
                            <div class="card card-sm">
                                <a class="card-img card-img-md" href="video-post.html">
                                    <img src="https://i1.ytimg.com/vi/{{ video.id }}/maxresdefault.jpg" alt="{{ video.title }}">
                                    <div class="card-meta">
                                        <span>{{ video.length }}</span>
                                    </div>
                                </a>
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h6 class="card-title"><a href="video-post.html">{{ video.title|slice(0, 38) }}</a></h6>
                                    <p class="card-text font-size-md">{{ video.text|slice(0, 100) ~ '...' }}</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card-footer">
                                    <span><i class="ya ya-clock"></i> {{ video.date|date("M d, Y") }}</span>
                                    <span class="ml-auto"><i class="ya ya-eye"></i> {{ video.views }} views</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <!-- end .card -->
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white border-top border-bottom px-3">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row justify-content-around align-items-center">
                <div class="col-6">
                    <div class="embed-player embed-player-lg">
                        <div class="embed-img">
                            <img src="https://static.giantbomb.com/uploads/original/0/8169/3028105-screenshot+%2862%29.png" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <div class="embed-icon">
                            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dw_oH5oiUSE" ya-lightbox>
                                <i class="ya ya-play"></i>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-5 pl-5 mr-auto">
                    <h2 class="h1 font-weight-semibold text-dark mb-3">Premium Videos for Our Members</h2>
                    <p class="mb-4 pb-2">Received the likewise law graceful his. Nor might set along charm now equal green. <br>Pleased yet equally correct colonel not one. Say anxious carried compact conduct <br>ps4 general nay certain.</p>
                    <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg mr-1" href="pricing.html" role="button">View our plans</a>
                    <a class="btn btn-outline btn-lg" href="register.html" role="button">Create an account <i class="ya ya-user-add"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-6">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-8 mx-auto text-center mb-4">
                    <i class="ya ya-question icon"></i>
                    <h2 class="font-size-lg">Frequently asked questions</h2>
                    <p>Resolution possession discovered surrounded advantages has but few add. Yet walls times spoil put be it reserved contempt rendered smallest.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-11 mx-auto">
                    <div class="row">
                        {% for faq in faq[0]['answer'] %}
                            {% if loop.index < 5 %}
                                <div class="col-6 card-group">
                                    <div class="card mb-4">
                                        <h6 class="card-header">{{ faq.title }}</h6>
                                        <div class="card-body">
                                            <p class="card-text">{{ faq.text|slice(0, 160) }}...</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            {% endif %}
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center mt-4">
                <a class="btn btn-outline btn-lg" href="faq.html" role="button">Learn more</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-dark py-2">
        <div class="container-fluid px-2">
            <div class="owl-carousel" ya-carousel="autoplay: true;items: 5;margin: 8;nav: false;dots: false">
                {% for video in videos %}
                    {% if loop.index < 16 %}
                        <div class="embed-player">
                            <img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/{{ video.id }}/maxresdefault.jpg" alt="">
                            <div class="embed-icon embed-icon-dark">
                                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v={{ video.id}}" ya-lightbox><i class="ya ya-play"></i></a>
                            </div>
                            <div class="embed-caption">
                                <div class="embed-length">{{ video.length }}</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
{% endblock %}
